{"tid":1657367,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"放寬按揭樓價上限  首置人士買800萬樓可借9成按揭","createTime":"2019-10-16T05:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T10:14:25.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d94bac001a09ac1a9429f109eadd7ad0695546f","tid":1657367,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"推高樓價.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥原定今日（16日）早上11時於立法會宣讀任內第三份施政報告，林鄭月娥強調房屋問題是重中之重，除了放寬未來公私營房屋比例由6：4轉為7：3，她更宣佈為協助首次置業人士，將放寬按揭保險計劃的樓價上限，首置人士可申請最高9成按貸的樓價上限由現時400萬元提升至800萬元。<br />\n另外，最高8按揭貸款的樓價上限則由600萬元提升至1,000萬元，後者可以包括自用樓換樓按揭。<br />\n現行的按揭保險計劃下，市民可以透過按揭保險申請高成數按揭貸款，以減輕首期上車的壓力。按照現時規定，首間自...<a href=\"https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=113850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwl%26id%3D113850&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=bc821d53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=113850</a>"},{"pid":"0c8b008311ef9cb348463ea65869c25a9f5a65ec","tid":1657367,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0a473abe63cb2f5a90b8505e6b27d9651505257a","tid":1657367,"uid":160102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"接地產商廢老貨"},{"pid":"30a8e463af2fd753203c840a4248424ed3a13d53","tid":1657367,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"唉。。。又升。"}]}